      "kind": "content",
      "html": "<p><b>Jimmy:</b> What are you doing on Saturday evening, Sophie?<br><b>Sophie:</b> I&rsquo;m not sure yet. I might be going out but I haven&rsquo;t made any plans. Why are you asking?<br><b>Jimmy:</b> <b>(1)</b><br><b>Sophie:</b> Oh, I&rsquo;d love to. That sounds like a great event. Is it a formal occasion?<br><b>Jimmy:</b> <b>(2)</b><br><b>Sophie:</b> Yes, that&rsquo;s perfect. I&rsquo;ll be there right on time! What are you going to cook?<br><b>Jimmy:</b> <b>(3)</b><br><b>Sophie:</b> Well, to be honest, I don&rsquo;t really like it - I had a bad experience once. If I had a choice, I&rsquo;d go for something else.<br><b>Jimmy:</b> <b>(4)</b><br><b>Sophie:</b> No, no, I&rsquo;m not. I like trying vegetarian dishes now and then, but I do enjoy eating meat.<br><b>Jimmy:</b> <b>(5)</b><br><b>Sophie:</b> Yes, absolutely! I love them, especially with a good mix of cheese, pickles and crispy bacon.<br><b>Jimmy:</b> <b>(6)</b><br><b>Sophie:</b> Sure, I&rsquo;m really looking forward to it.</p>"
    },
